00:01:10.170 --> 00:01:11.420
DERAY MCKESSON: Appreciate it.

00:01:11.420 --> 00:01:12.461
It's an honor to be here.

00:01:12.461 --> 00:01:17.534
It's good to see some familiar
faces and so many new faces.

00:01:17.534 --> 00:01:18.950
This is embarrassing
for you, Ben,

00:01:18.950 --> 00:01:20.250
but I went to college with Ben!

00:01:20.250 --> 00:01:23.231
I saw Ben in the hallway
