00:43:29.910 --> 00:43:30.460
I don't know [INAUDIBLE].

00:43:30.460 --> 00:43:31.348
[LAUGHTER]

00:43:32.624 --> 00:43:33.290
A couple things.

00:43:33.290 --> 00:43:35.700
One is that this work
is often slow for people

00:43:35.700 --> 00:43:39.080
