these sort of deep things,

00:43:39.080 --> 00:43:40.860
right?

00:43:40.860 --> 00:43:43.310
I also think that some of
the most effective ways

00:43:43.310 --> 00:43:45.770
to change individual
people's hearts and mind

00:43:45.770 --> 00:43:48.150
is in private
sometimes, and then

00:43:48.150 --> 00:43:50.806
using examples that are
not necessarily about them,

00:43:50.806 --> 00:43:52.430
that they don't
realize are about them,

00:43:52.430 --> 00:43:53.890
but that are about them.

00:43:53.890 --> 00:43:56.560
So I think about people who say
