them, I can't believe

00:44:03.670 --> 00:44:06.680
that person said that, which
is really what they just said.

00:44:06.680 --> 00:44:09.044
And then we use that as
a launching pad and then

00:44:09.044 --> 00:44:11.460
sort of, at the end, get back
to like, you said that, too,

00:44:11.460 --> 00:44:14.710
